{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had never slept out in the mud with the mosquitoes and spiders and stuff like that, which is what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she-- and he was a real-- we got to where we just loved this guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was all man, boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "During the-- I remember during the machine-- when the men had to crawl through the defilade, barbed wire with machine guns shooting over your head, and that-- that scared everybody, you know, because if anybody makes-- the guns are locked, so they can't come down.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they're still shooting bullets 6 inches over your head-- machine gun bullets, and some of them are tracers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you can hear them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I tell you what, this guy was really sweating it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he-- when the time came for him to go, he went lickety split through there, barbed wire snags all over his face and each-- and he came out probably in the top three, time-wise, of guys that went through that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I am, because-- but I was going to say that the mystery-- some of these Jewish men were sent to the South Pacific.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- I've talked to them and talked to other guys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How come they won't let these-- I'd like to go into combat with these guys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, if we're going to have to go into combat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, they let them go to Germany because of the way the Germans treat the Jews, which I said, well, what the-- what is that about?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nobody really knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't think it was the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it was just eeny meeny miny mo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You go to the South Pacific because they need you down there, whatever the specialty was.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
